2005;;Brotherhood !The Brotherhood IV;;Canadian;;David DeCoteau;;Sebastian Gacki, April Telek;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Brotherhood_IV;;A young cadet at a military academy joins its secret society, the "Black Skulls". Sent to a strange cave on a nearby beach, he does not survive the ceremony, being attacked by a succubus with lightning powers. The mythical creature then goes after the other members of the society.